  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Screening of refractory defect is one of major reason for amblyopy. Photorefraction is a new
      method with some advantages in treatment of this problem. In this study the investigators are
      going to compare the results of this surgery in children between 1 to 10 years old with
      cycloautorefraction in children above 3 years old.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
